                    These terms set forth the conditions for using this
                    portfolio website (the "Site") and the contents provided by
                    the creator "manpuc" (the "Creator"). By using this Site,
                    users are deemed to have agreed to these terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2>Article 2 (Prohibited Actions)</h2>
                <p>
                    Users shall not engage in the following acts when using the
                    Site:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Acts that interfere with or may interfere with the
                        operation of the Site.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Acts that infringe on the intellectual property rights,
                        such as copyrights or trademarks, of the Creator or any
                        third party.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Unauthorized access or acts that disrupt the functions
                        of the Site's servers or networks.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Commercial use (redistribution, resale, etc.) of the
                        Site's content without the Creator's permission.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Other acts that violate laws and regulations or public
                        order and morals.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2>Article 3 (Disclaimer)</h2>
                <p>
                    The Creator does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness,
                    or up-to-dateness of the information posted on the Site.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The Creator shall not be liable for any damage (direct or
                    indirect) caused by the use of the Site. Use of the
                    published source code or software is at your own risk.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2>Article 4 (Copyright)</h2>
                <p>
                    The copyright of all content on this Site (text, images,
                    published code, etc.) belongs to the Creator unless
                    otherwise specified. Unauthorized reproduction, reprinting,
                    modification, or distribution beyond the scope of private
                    use is prohibited.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Article 5 (Changes to Terms)</h2>
                <p>
                    The Creator may change these terms at any time without
                    notice if deemed necessary. The changed terms shall be
                    effective from the time they are posted on the Site.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
